    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim your <strong>green beans</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>trimmed green beans </strong>to a large piece of <strong>tin foil</strong> (or two!) with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water </strong>and a small knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Scrunch the foil around the<strong> </strong>green beans to form a tightly sealed parcel[s], then add<strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>to a separate tray[s] and put it in the oven for 10-12 min or until the beans are tender with a slight bite</p>",
